{"tid":681412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"上星期去婚前檢查, 個姑娘好撚串","createTime":"2018-05-28T04:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T07:20:14.000Z","uid":22839,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1030e51d8fac52f9bbe48822cad62f0cb191b72f","tid":681412,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"邊一個診所唔講喇<br />\n<br />\n登記完<br />\n排一陣去抽血<br />\n抽完血<br />\n行返出去櫃位<br />\n另一個姑娘比咗我樽仔我驗精<br />\n佢話一個鐘頭內交返嚟<br />\n如果唔係就唔新鮮<br />\n<br />\n我望住個空樽 (大約藥丸樽size)<br />\n問佢要幾多<br />\n佢唔理我<br />\n我再問佢<br />\n佢啤撚住我話<br />\n&quot;你鐘意咪入滿囉&quot;<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味咁撚串<br />\n臭閪<br />\n我就入滿比佢睇<br />\n即刻走咗去樓下商場個殘廁<br />\n扲住個手機睇住啲護士AV起勢咁打<br />\n手都唔洗<br />\n個樽仔好滿之餘<br />\n個蓋都仲沾住幾滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我就入返診所<br />\n專登唔搵膠袋入住<br />\n成枝又暖又滿咁隊返比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一星期後<br />\n出咗報告<br />\n醫生話我啲精好唔活躍<br />\n大家覺得姑娘係咪做咗啲咩手腳?"},{"pid":"059143f003d977166913dae36f88e3b54da32a79","tid":681412,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e089ac15473aa7625a66c3cee67b866b50e985bb","tid":681412,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"其實係個男醫生吞咗先求其俾個藉口你"},{"pid":"5bb0ae69ec858e291df31874dfb5d3d394783eed","tid":681412,"uid":11512,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"其實係個男護士吞咗先求其俾個藉口你"},{"pid":"df933945ac1a79b5ba99db977027fa41bddb4b5c","tid":681412,"uid":128057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"係咪你問得太淫賤？<br />\n一係就姑娘自己心邪"},{"pid":"c6bf1af379d4c4d9856189ef8dda0a686a47859a","tid":681412,"uid":125731,"like":0,